org.omg.CORBA
Class PrimitiveKind

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.omg.CORBA.PrimitiveKind
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDLEntity, java.io.Serializable
public final class PrimitiveKind
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDLEntity

In CORBA, there are primitive types as for example : long, double, float, and so on. This enumeration provides an identifier for each primitive type.
